{"title": "He Fell in Love with His Wife", "description": "James desperately needs someone to help him keep his farm going, but has failure after colossal failure finding a good housekeeper. Alida marries a man only to find out he's already married. She's so undone when she finds out that she just wants to go somewhere where no one will judge her for her misfortune, where she can work and keep herself fed and clothed. James and Alida meet and arrange for a strictly business marriage, leaving loving and honoring out of the vows. The title of the book tells the rest of the story, but the way it gets there is worth the journey. (Introduction by TriciaG)", "duration": 38041, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "9990", "name": "Edward P. Roe"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/LibrivoxCdCoverArt33/hefellinlovewithhiswife_1311.jpg", "copyright_year": "1886", "genres": ["Romance"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "TriciaG"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Left Alone", "readers": [8138], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/hefellinlove_1310_librivox/hefellinlovewithhiswife_01_roe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1039}, {"section": 2, "title": "A Very Interested Friend", "readers": [8337], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/hefellinlove_1310_librivox/hefellinlovewithhiswife_02_roe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1605}, {"section": 3, "title": "Mrs. Mumpson Negotiates and Yields", "readers": [8138], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/hefellinlove_1310_librivox/hefellinlovewithhiswife_03_roe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1251}, {"section": 4, "title": "Domestic Bliss", "readers": [8138], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/hefellinlove_1310_librivox/hefellinlovewithhiswife_04_roe_64kb.mp3", "duration": 776}, {"section": 5, "title": "Mrs. Mumpson Takes up Her Burdens", "readers": [8138], "